  <prompt>
    Deploy Phase 4 work to the development environment: invoke `bff-deploy` for `Sprk.Bff.Api` and `code-page-deploy` for the `SpaarkeAi` code page (which carries the ContextPane `memory`-channel subscriber from task 098 + the layered context cards from tasks 076-079). Verify post-deploy health via `/ping` + smoke-test of recall + promotion flow.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform release engineer. Familiar with `bff-deploy` and `code-page-deploy` skills + Azure App Service deployment.</role>

  <goal>
    BFF API deployed to `bff-dev` App Service; SpaarkeAi code page deployed to Dataverse; post-deploy smoke tests confirm endpoint health, recall flow, and promotion-event delivery. Deploy artifacts archived with publish-size delta vs prior baseline.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Phase 4 added: upload-pipeline enrichment services (4-B), composition refactor (4-E), 8 tool handlers (4-G + 4-H), promotion workflow (4-K + 4-L), ContextPane subscriber (4-M), workspace Q8 conflict check (4-N), Tier 5 retrieval (4-O), audit-repo rename (4-P), verification (4-Q), tests (4-R 103). This task is the deploy half of wave 4-R, paired with 103. Deploy skills handle environment selection + secret resolution.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/</file>
      <file>src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/</file>
      <file>scripts/deploy/</file>
      <file>deploy/</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Per-task BFF publish-size measurement; report delta vs Phase 3 baseline.</constraint>
    <constraint source="azure-deployment.md">Deploy to bff-dev first; production gating happens via Phase 7 wrap-up.</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md">Verify no new HIGH-severity CVE from `dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Use `npm install --legacy-peer-deps --no-audit --no-fund` for Vite code-page (NOT `npm ci`) per CLAUDE.md §11.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Tier-1 logging review on deployed instance — App Insights query confirms no content leakage.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/spec.md</file>
